Package com.github.naoghuman.lib.tag.internal Description

Contains the default Implementation from the library Lib-Tag.

The preferred way is not to create an instance directly with the classes in this package. Plz use instead the corresponding fluent builders in the package com.github.naoghuman.lib.tag.core.
